### Custom dependency injection
``` javascript
// PeopleService.js
export default function PeopleService({ fetch }) {
  this.getPeople = (id) =>
    fetch(`http://swapi.co/api/people/${id}/`)
      .then(res => res.json());
}
```
Note:
- destructure dependency object

